---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <title>Privacy Policy - Arrivo</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-white">
<main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-24 prose prose-slate">
    <a href="/" class="text-primary font-semibold mb-8 inline-block">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">Last updated: January 2026</p>

    <p class="mb-6">
        Arrivo ("the app") is designed with privacy in mind. This policy explains what information
        is collected and how it is used.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
        The app allows users to input specific data to track Amtrak trains, including:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>Train Numbers</li>
        <li>Station Codes (e.g., CHI, NYP)</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-6">
        This data is stored locally on your device and is only used to query third-party APIs
        for realtime status information. As I do not personally operate either of these APIs, please refer to their
        privacy
        policies for further information on how your data is used.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">2. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
        Arrivo retrieves data from unofficial and community-run APIs:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>
            <strong><a href="https://www.amtrak.com/track-your-train.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline">Amtrak API</a>:</strong>
            The default provider for train statuses used by the official Amtrak Track a Train Map.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong><a href="https://amtraker.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline">Amtraker API</a>:</strong>
            A fast, community-run alternative for realtime data.
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Security</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
        We do not use any tracking cookies or analytics platforms. Your tracked trains and
        stations remain private to your device.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">4. Contact</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
        For questions regarding this policy, please contact me via GitHub or email.
    </p>
</main>
</body>
</html>